                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Bards swarm kite which could be called charm kiting. Which is exactly as you describe and it is no less effective than it ever was. Add an insta cast invis and it gets very sick. They can get the pet down to a few percent of health and break it when they want to rather than starting at a point that will *probably* find the pet at a few percent of health.
<br />

<br />
The only problem they have is if the swarm is too large then the pet dies too fast if they don't have insta-clicky invis.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Max
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=368646" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fanamax the Enchanter</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
